reviews.review_text: yes um nice best of both worlds,  you can hear the audience well, the sound of the room and reverbs,  but  all the bass is good and clear,  good show,  and good sound quality/ i give 5 stars for the cold rain and snow,  nice quality of the great one's voice

great show, excellent aud source credit to tony suraci for this aud -- i think its best sounding and most dynamic of all auds offered...

and credit to the band -- this show kicks ass and there's just one thing to call it: "a jerry show"

jerry's on his game all night with stellar guitar work and vocals.

check out that birdsong -- a true monster :-)
